FBIS4-59950 "drnes097_s_94013" FBIS-NES-94-097 Daily Report 17 May 1994 Iran Tajik Government, Opposition To Meet in Tehran Tajik Government, Opposition To Meet in Tehran NC1705075194 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network in Persian 0230 GMT 17 May 94 NC1705075194 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network Persian BFN [Text] Talks between the Tajik Government and opposition are to start in Tehran on 4 June. In an interview, a Tajik opposition leader said that the topics to be discussed by the two sides have been discussed with UN representatives and agreed upon. He also expressed the opposition's readiness to sign a provisional cease-fire agreement.
